@startuml
title Physical Resources Management API – System Sequence Diagram

actor Client
boundary "Physical Resources API" as System

== Get All ==
Client -> System : GET /api/PhysicalResource
System --> Client : 200 OK\nList<PhysicalResourceDTO>

== Get By ID ==
Client -> System : GET /api/PhysicalResource/get/{id}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nPhysicalResourceDTO\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found

== Get By Code ==
Client -> System : GET /api/PhysicalResource/get/code/{code}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nPhysicalResourceDTO\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found

== Get By Description ==
Client -> System : GET /api/PhysicalResource/get/description/{description}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nList<PhysicalResourceDTO>\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found

== Get By Status ==
Client -> System : GET /api/PhysicalResource/get/status/{status}
note right
status ∈ { Available, Unavailable, UnderMaintenance }
end note
System --> Client : 200 OK\nList<PhysicalResourceDTO>\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found

== Get By Type ==
Client -> System : GET /api/PhysicalResource/get/type/{type}
note right
type ∈ { STSCrane, YGCrane, MCrane, Truck, Forklift, RStacker, SCarrier, TugBoat, Other }
end note
System --> Client : 200 OK\nList<PhysicalResourceDTO>\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found

== Get By Qualification ==
Client -> System : GET /api/PhysicalResource/get/qualification/{qualificationId}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nList<PhysicalResourceDTO>\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found

== Create ==
Client -> System : POST /api/PhysicalResource\nBody: CreatingPhysicalResourceDto
System --> Client : 201 Created\nPhysicalResourceDTO\n-- OR --\n400 Bad Request

== Update (PATCH) ==
Client -> System : PATCH /api/PhysicalResource/update/{id}\nBody: { description?, operationalCapacity?, setupTime?, qualificationId? }
System --> Client : 200 OK\nPhysicalResourceDTO\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found\n-- OR --\n400 Bad Request\n{ error: "The following field(s) cannot be updated", fields: [...] }

== Deactivate ==
Client -> System : PATCH /api/PhysicalResource/deactivate/{id}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nPhysicalResourceDTO\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found\n-- OR --\n400 Bad Request\n{ error: "The physical resource is already deactivated." }

== Reactivate ==
Client -> System : PATCH /api/PhysicalResource/reactivate/{id}
System --> Client : 200 OK\nPhysicalResourceDTO\n-- OR --\n404 Not Found\n-- OR --\n400 Bad Request\n{ error: "The physical resource is already active." }

@enduml
